    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, representing the pinnacle of automotive care. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, showroom-quality shine with no scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the interior is pristine, with leather that looks and feels brand new and every electronic component functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no signs of wear. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is essentially in 'as-new' condition, perfect for a collector or a discerning buyer who demands the very best.",
