    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next big adventure with a new owner! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
