      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical maintenance has been prioritized, including a comprehensive VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high torque loads. The chassis remains sharp with refreshed bushings and a factory-spec limited-slip differential providing excellent mid-corner traction. While the aesthetic shows honest signs of use, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are dialed in for peak performance. A true driver's car with the mechanical pedigree to match.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
