    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains its deep luster with only minor road wear consistent with careful use, and the alloy wheels are free of major scuffs. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary featuring supple leather seating, pristine carpets, and a fully functional suite of modern technology and climate controls. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including a recent professional multi-point inspection and oil change. With a clean title and a history of preventative maintenance, this car is ready for its next owner to drive with absolute confidence.",
      "price": 36500.0,
